nodes.text: A Twi'lek female Jedi Master served the Jedi Order around the year 4000 BBY. She was one of the Four Masters who built a new Jedi Temple on Coruscant following the devastation of Ossus and the Great Jedi Library located there during the Old Sith Wars. Along with the three other founding Jedi Masters, the Twi'lek was immortalized through a bas-relief sculpted in a massive pylon displayed at the main entrance to the Temple.
